Will create the boilerplate for the serverless.yml

$ serverless create -t aws-ruby -p yourServiceName

++++ make sure you aws keys are set in ypur terminal  ++++

$ sls deploy 

Create a gemfile and add the required gems you want


$ docker run --rm -it -v $PWD:/var/gem_build -w /var/gem_build lambci/lambda:build-ruby2.5 bundle install --path=.





